

**Matsh am gawul i e chehgi g Jesus ha wui. **

*An g neid g Mark 9:2-13; Luke 9:28-36 *

1 D am d i chuhdp tash amjed. D g Jesus ab i ha wai g Peter ch James ch John. D am wehmaj ab i chehchsh hema uhgk doꞌag t ab k atsh gan hu dada doꞌag dahm. 2 Kutsh g Jesus am hahawa gawul e juh. Sh g wuhioshaj hab waꞌi masma tonod mo g tash ch g wehschugaj hab masma s‑tohta mo g tonlig. 3 Kutsh ab haha wabsh i e chehgi g Mosesbad ch Elijabad k am wehmaj neneok g Jesus. 

4 Sh g Peter hab kaij ab wui g Jesus, “T‑kownalig, s‑apꞌe oki mach ia haꞌichug. Kutt ia waik wo ha chuhcha g al chechopi matt hekaj ab wo si has em‑el ahpi ch Mosesbad ch Elijabad maptp wo tatchuad.” 

5 Neh, sh am wabsh kia neok g Peter. Kutsh g si s‑mahs chewagi ab i wuhshani k ab ehka ha dahm. Tsh g Jiosh neꞌoki ab kaida chewagi t amjed k hab kaij, “Jesus o d si ni‑tatchuidch ni‑alidag. Heg amt ab wo si kaihamad.” 

6 Kutsh si s‑ehbeni hegam Peter am i kahk g neꞌoki k am wabsh si kupal shul jewedo. 

7 Tsh am hahawa jiwia g Jesus k an ha tahtam k hab kaij, “Gegokiwuio. Pi g wo shaꞌi e todsid.” 

8 Tsh am hahawa i chum nenhog. Kush heg waꞌi Jesus hejel am kehk. Sh pi am hu haꞌichug hegam gohk. 

9 Sh ab hahawa i huhudkhim doꞌag t amjed. Sh ab si ha chehani g Jesus ch hab kaij, “Pi g am hedai wo shaꞌi ahgid mamt haschu nei, nt hoꞌip kia uhpam i wuhsh ab muhkig amjed ahni Jiosh si Kehsha.” 

10 Kush hab kaij idam ab wui g Jesus, “Neh, bo chechꞌe hegam chehanig t‑mashchamdam matsh ia wehpeg wo e maskogi g Elijabad. Tsh g Jiosh si Kehsha ia haha wo e maskogi. Pegih, t haschu ahgk pi ia wehpeg m‑baꞌich e maskogi hegai Elijabad?” 

11 Sh hab kaij g Jesus, “Hema at woho wehpeg wo e maskogid k hab wo masmak mash wa g Elijabad ch wehs haꞌichu wo i apꞌech. 12 Kunt wo em‑ahgi mat wa woho heki hu jiwia. K Wabshaba muꞌijj pi mahch mo hedai wud ch ab wui hab wabsh juh g pi ap e‑tatchui. Pegih, k e aihim mat hab waꞌap wo ni‑juh k wo ni‑shoꞌigch ahni Jiosh si Kehsha.” 

13 Kutsh am hahawa i amich idam moki heg hab ahg John mat wa am i shonwuich g pahl wakona. 

**Matsh g Jesus gam hu hab i juh g jiawul ab amjed g ali **

*An g neid g Mark 9:14-29; Luke 9:37-43a *

14 D eda muꞌi hemajkam am haꞌichug amai machd am wih. Kud am uhpam dada hegam Jesus. D ab hema i tonwua Jesus wui 15 k hab kaij, “Ab g si i s‑hoꞌigeꞌid g ni‑sulijga. Si o pi ap mumku ch hebai am wabsh s‑e chuchkagid ch muꞌikko am gegshe nahda ch ed o am shuhdagi ch ed. 16 Kunt ia chum uꞌapa ha wui idam m‑chuhchai. T pi e nako mas wo doaj.” 

17 D hab kaij g Jesus ab t‑wui, “Shoꞌo waꞌi pi geꞌej g em‑wohochudadag. M im hu hab wabsh i si e Juhkch ab ni‑amjed. Shahag wepo mant tash ia wo em‑wehmajkad ch wo em‑nakogad mat haha wo i geꞌeda.” Bad kaij g Jesus ch hab hahawa ahg hegai oꞌodham, “Ab g i bekaꞌi g e‑alidag.” 18 D ab hahawa i bei wui. D g Jesus am si s‑gewkam chehani g jiawul mat gam hu hab wo i e juh. Kud wa woho hab e juh. D am ha hekaj wabsh i doa g ali. 

19 Kuchd ab hahawa hejelko kakke g Jesus machs haschu ahgk ahchim pi t‑nako matt gam hu hab wo i juh g jiawul. 

20 D hab kaij g Jesus, “Heg amt hekaj pi e nako mam pi ab hu wohochud mat hab wo e juh. Nt wo si shel em‑ahgi mamt wo e nakog k wabsh chum haschu hab wo juh mamt hab wo chei s‑wohochudch mat hab wo e juh. Chum at hems g geꞌe doꞌag gan hu hab wo i kekiwua mamt wabsh wo ahgi s‑wohochudch mat hab wo e juh. \[ 21 T wabshaba ihda hab mahs haꞌichu hab waꞌi masma gm hu hab wo i juh mamt wo si e hoꞌigeꞌidahunad Jiosh wui pi haꞌichu koꞌadch.\]” 

**Mash g Jesus am ep ha ahgid ab amjed g e‑muhkig **

*An g neid g Mark 9:30-32; Luke 9:43b-45 *

22 Am achd wabsh kia oiopo Galilee chekshani ch ed. D hab kaij g Jesus ab t‑wui, “E o aihim mat wo ni‑bei hegam mo s‑ni‑kehꞌid k ab wo ni‑dagito 23 mant wo ni‑muhkid. T wabshaba am wo him k d wo i waik tashk amjed. Nt ab wo uhpam i wuhsh muhkig amjed.” 

Neh, kuchd wehsijj si pi ap t‑taht am i kaiok ihda. 

**Matsh has masma ha namkid g Jesus g geꞌe cheopi kowlanta **

24 Kuchd ged hu dada Capernaum t am. D am hema jiwia Peter wui hegam mo an hemapad g cheopi kowlanta k ab kakke ch hab kaij, “No ha namkid g cheopi kowlanta g em‑mashchamdam?” 

25 D hab kaij g Peter, “Hemho wa,” K amjed ged hu i wah kih ch ed. 

D g Jesus ab ha hekaj kakke ch hab kaij, “Simon Peter, nap hab elid mat g kokownal ab wo haꞌichu ha kowlant hegam mo d ha wehm kihkam?” 

26 D hab kaij g Peter, “Piaꞌa.” 

D hab ep kaij g Jesus, “Pegih, t heg hekaj pi haꞌichu wo ni‑kowlant g Jiosh. 27 Ch wabshaba pi tatchua machs wo ha kudu idam hemajkam. Kupt heg hekaj am wo hih shuhdagi wui k am wo wua g waptopi hukshpakud. Kut g si wehpeg watopi mapt wo huksh g lial ab wo kamshchid mat wo ai hegai cheopi kowlanta an ni‑wehhejed ch ep m‑wehhejed. Pt am wo be k hekaj wo ha namkid.” 

